title: Minutemen Scans Week of 04.09.08 (early edition)
description:
A new week begins and some nice comics arrive. The current Wolverine and Fantastic Four arcs are awesome and my favorite space book, Nova, came out. This is going to be a light week, not a lot is released this week. So here are the books that hit the store shelves Wednesday. Monday's torrent will be full of back issues.

A few notes, Amazing Spider-Girl's cover has a misprint on it. The cover list the issue as issue 17 when in fact it's issue 19. And for those wondering, the Skrull face Variants releases are just the variant covers. The books were released in past packs. The Promo Card is just that, a little promo card for upcoming series they give out at you LCS.

Enjoy these new books. See you Monday.
